Then when you realised I am not going to quit server, you simply tried to make life of my friends or even people I simply was in zone with miserable. People that not only never done anything to MiM, but weren't even part of war that your guild started.<br>
<br>
Your guild PKed Orraden 8 times because he was doing minis in BoT and I helped him a few times. 8 times your members simply PKed someone in zone they &quot;thought&quot; I was friends with and never returned any of his droppable gear they ganked. Not even apologies were served when officers told members Orraden wasn't KoS. I am not surprised he finally snapped. Your guild probably ganked up to 50k worth of gear off him.<br>
