What about Mediman whom Ubertanka kept attacking for days despite direct officer's orders? Ubertanka simply zoned into BoT fully buffed, trained group where Mediman was and attacked him instead of me (I guess we look alike?). Not once, not twice, day after day. I was &quot;kos&quot; and standing right there. Mediman wasn't and it was confirmed by MiM officers, yet Ubertanka kept training and attacking HIM (no he didn't heal me, in fact I always disbanded group if MiM zoned in) and then training everyone at entrance when he got low on HP from me.<br>
