<br>
You know, of our two guilds, ours fights to defend ourselves and tried to resolve KoS issues numerous times. We don't gank innocent bystanders, we don't corpsecamp exp. loss corpses and we dont try to bully pople out of server. We don't try to spread propaganda all over server. And most of all we don't get PKers to help us fight you.<br>
<br>
Your guild ganks people for gear and says &quot;guildwar&quot; then when they been told they are wrong by their own officers doesn't return items ganked. Your guild bullies people and tries to make game not fun. Your guild cheats, trains and spreads lies about us.<br>
